WEBVTT

03:30.377 --> 03:32.921
- Daddy! Can I go to the pool?

03:33.005 --> 03:35.257
- Yes, but be careful.

13:36.191 --> 13:40.070
Tell me, did she have
previous concussions?

13:40.153 --> 13:41.154
- No.

13:41.238 --> 13:42.197
- No.

13:42.281 --> 13:44.157
- I don’t know.

13:44.616 --> 13:46.577
- Allergic reactions to
medications?

13:46.660 --> 13:47.786
- No.

13:50.205 --> 13:54.668
- Well... We can do
a CT scan... if you want.

15:56.206 --> 15:57.749
Whiskey?

16:26.403 --> 16:28.113
Want to tell?

16:32.784 --> 16:37.789
- One patient, a girl.
Her CT is the same as...

16:37.873 --> 16:39.750
- Will you be able to help her?

16:41.543 --> 16:44.171
- The second shot was normal.

16:46.340 --> 16:48.592
Hmmm... that's it.

16:48.675 --> 16:50.052
How are you?

16:50.135 --> 16:52.012
- My affairs?

16:52.095 --> 16:54.097
Nobody asks the bartender
about his business.

16:54.181 --> 16:55.807
They tell him theirs.

16:57.893 --> 16:59.228
- Cheers.

23:02.090 --> 23:04.760
- Kolya, hey!... I told you!
Hey... what’s this!...

23:04.843 --> 23:06.553
- What’s going on?
This is a mess!

23:06.845 --> 23:08.555
- You... come in ... Sorry!

23:09.598 --> 23:11.350
Come on, pick it up!
Well, we have taps.

23:11.558 --> 23:13.602
- Well, and who pays?
It’s from your salary.

23:14.853 --> 23:18.315
- What have I got to do with it?
I'm just stuck, that's all.

23:23.320 --> 23:24.863
- You can! Come on! Hey!...
- Ok.

57:04.007 --> 57:06.802
- Anton!
- Sorry, we are closed.

57:08.804 --> 57:11.306
Ah, it’s you.

57:12.349 --> 57:14.226
- I need a drink.

57:15.435 --> 57:18.522
- Can I offer you
something special?

57:21.483 --> 57:24.361
Thirty years of whiskey,
cures everything.

57:24.444 --> 57:26.613
Soft, fragrant.

57:26.697 --> 57:28.198
You’ll like it!

57:30.409 --> 57:32.786
At the expense of the
institution.

57:39.042 --> 57:40.919
- Will you give me ice?

57:41.003 --> 57:42.379
- This one is just clean.

57:55.350 --> 57:56.685
Bad day?

57:59.104 --> 58:00.397
- Can I have more?

1:20:12.437 --> 1:20:15.357
- Come on, come on. Come in.
Come on, be careful.

1:20:19.152 --> 1:20:22.406
- Enough, enough,
enough, enough!

1:20:24.700 --> 1:20:26.910
Get ready for reanimation!

1:20:26.994 --> 1:20:30.205
- No, no, you can't come here.
Wait, please, there.

1:20:31.957 --> 1:20:34.251
- They will take care of her,
ma'am.

1:20:34.334 --> 1:20:36.170
Try to calm down.

1:20:36.253 --> 1:20:38.255
Everything will be fine.

1:20:46.180 --> 1:20:48.765
One, two!... Three!...

1:22:08.095 --> 1:22:09.763
- How are you?

1:22:09.847 --> 1:22:12.224
- Some water?
- No!

1:25:11.612 --> 1:25:13.614
You can't go there!

1:26:59.720 --> 1:27:01.722
- She has a cardiac arrest.

1:27:01.805 --> 1:27:03.807
- Prepare a defibrillator.
- Calm down!

1:27:04.266 --> 1:27:06.894
Warning! Discharge!

1:27:13.692 --> 1:27:15.903
- The heart did not start.

1:27:16.195 --> 1:27:17.571
- Let's do one more time.

1:27:17.654 --> 1:27:20.199
Warning! Discharge!

1:27:24.661 --> 1:27:26.830
How much time has passed?

1:27:26.914 --> 1:27:28.957
- Thirty seconds.

1:27:29.041 --> 1:27:31.126
- Raise it.
- Ok.

1:27:34.755 --> 1:27:37.591
Discharge!

1:27:37.674 --> 1:27:39.384
- We lose her.

1:27:42.846 --> 1:27:44.681
You can't come here!
Who are you?

1:27:44.765 --> 1:27:46.099
Listen, we are...

1:27:57.736 --> 1:27:59.530
- Attention! The heart started!

1:27:59.613 --> 1:28:01.406
Get parents out of here.
- Prepare oxygen!

1:28:01.490 --> 1:28:02.866
Please take off your hands...
- Come on, come on!...

1:28:03.116 --> 1:28:04.868
- Attention! Attention!
- Where is the oxygen mask?

1:28:04.952 --> 1:28:07.829
- Get away!
- Wait, wait, wait.

1:28:08.497 --> 1:28:10.874
- Where's the mask?
- Give me the mask, faster!

1:28:10.958 --> 1:28:13.627
- The mask!
- Here you go.

1:28:15.921 --> 1:28:18.590
- All right. It works!

1:29:13.687 --> 1:29:15.439
- Now I am free, Mommy.

1:29:20.819 --> 1:29:22.529
- Forgive me.

1:29:25.532 --> 1:29:26.867
- I love you.

1:29:32.539 --> 1:29:33.916
- I love you, too, my baby.

1:29:37.628 --> 1:29:39.755
I miss you so much.
